# Expanding Belonging in Computer Science

## Stereotypes in Computer Science

#### Why is it so important to attend to your students' sense of belonging? Like many science, technology, engineering, and math (STEM) fields, computer science has long been associated with a specific stereotype of a person. Look at the representations of IT professionals and software engineers. What do you notice?

